<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ن ي ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٢٩٦ - ن ي ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نيَّرَ ينيِّر، تَنْيِيرًا، فهو مُنَيِّر، والمفعول مُنَيَّر<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• نَيَّر الثَّوبَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - نارَه، جعل له نِيرًا أي صُورًا وخطوطًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - جعل له لُحْمَةً <span class="c2">(خيوط النَّسْج العَرْضيّة)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>